member.name: IEnumAssocHandlers.Next
member.summary: Retrieves a specified number of elements.
member.param: The number of elements to retrieve.
When this method returns, contains the address of an array of pointers. Each IAssocHandler represents a single handler.
When this method returns, contains a pointer to the number of elements retrieved.
member.returns: If this method succeeds, it returns S_OK. Otherwise, it returns an HRESULT error code.

member.name: IEnumAssocHandlers
member.summary: Exposes a method that allows enumeration of a collection of handlers associated with particular file name extensions.
